data.description: Welcome to Palmetto Pointe Townes! Boasting an open concept downstairs - perfect for hosting get-togethers! Kitchen is spacious with matching stainless steel appliances and granite countertops that flows into the living room that is filled with natural lighting and overlooks a wooded backyard for privacy. LVP throughout the entire main level. Head upstairs to where there are 3 spacious bedrooms. There are 2 bedrooms with a full bathroom in between, and a large primary bedroom with an extra large closet! Perfectly located next to schools and shopping! Easy commute to Savannah, Old Town Bluffton, HHI, and Parris Island / MCAS.
